                  1.6.95     1.6.95     1.1.96     1.1.98     1.1.96
                     old        old        new        new        new
                per cent   per cent   per cent   per cent   per cent
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Glass                 42         72         40         70         70
Tinplate              26         72         30         70         70
Aluminium             18         72         20         70         70
Board/card/paper      18         64         20         50         60
