<HEADLINE>
FT  22 JAN 94 / Finance and the Family: Bradford &amp; Bingley
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Bradford &amp; Bingley has relaunched its 30-day Direct Notice postal account.
Interest rates are 6.35 per cent gross on Pounds 1,000-Pounds 9,999; 6.85
per cent gross on Pounds 10,000-Pounds 24,999 and 7.1 per cent on balances
of Pounds 25,000 and above.
There is also a monthly income option of 6.65 per cent on balances of Pounds
10,000 and above. The rates are 6.65 per cent gross (Pounds 10,000-Pounds
24,999) and 6.9 per cent gross on Pounds 25,000 and above.
</TEXT>
